PrecisAmendments to the TAX COLLECTION AGREEMENTS AND FEDERAL POST-SECONDARY EDUCATION AND HEALTH CONTRIBUTIONS REGULATIONS, 1987 which provide for adjustments to be made to the Canada Health and Social Transfer payments to the provinces in cases where there were under-payments or over-payments made under the former Established Program Financing.
